771
01:10:32.583 --> 01:10:36.541
They say it's not a problem.
If she trains at least for two weeks...

772
01:10:36.625 --> 01:10:38.250
I know her, Braulio.

773
01:10:38.333 --> 01:10:40.458
Damn, Mariel! Fuck!

774
01:10:48.416 --> 01:10:51.791
I'd leave everything for you, Mariel.
I swear.

775
01:10:58.250 --> 01:11:00.708
Flex here.

776
01:11:01.875 --> 01:11:03.750
That's right!

777
01:11:03.833 --> 01:11:06.166
Long. Push the platform.

778
01:11:06.708 --> 01:11:07.708
Very good.

779
01:11:12.208 --> 01:11:13.541
Good, Mariel. Come on!

780
01:11:14.375 --> 01:11:16.333
Come on, stretch your leg.

781
01:11:22.500 --> 01:11:24.666
Push it in. That's right.

782
01:11:25.708 --> 01:11:27.250
Hard. That's right.

783
01:11:28.041 --> 01:11:29.916
Nadia is not training?

784
01:11:31.041 --> 01:11:32.583
Weren't we a team?

785
01:11:41.166 --> 01:11:45.541
Nadia has been working this whole time.
You're the one who has to catch up.

786
01:11:46.708 --> 01:11:51.833
Yes, but we're diving together,
and I have to train with her.

787
01:11:51.916 --> 01:11:56.000
No, honey, what you need is
to do what I tell you to, okay?

788
01:11:56.083 --> 01:12:00.666
- Braulio, I can...
- No. Who's the coach here? You?

789
01:12:02.250 --> 01:12:04.916
Mariel, will you tell us all what to do?

790
01:12:05.583 --> 01:12:07.833
Will you coach the team now?

791
01:12:08.541 --> 01:12:10.041
That's all I needed!

792
01:12:11.583 --> 01:12:15.250
I'm giving you a chance.
Don't push my buttons and get to work!

793
01:12:15.958 --> 01:12:19.583
No one is giving me a chance.
I'm here because I've earned it.

794
01:12:21.166 --> 01:12:22.166
Get down!

795
01:12:23.666 --> 01:12:26.083
Get down from the platform right now!

796
01:12:26.791 --> 01:12:29.458
Get down, Mariel!
I'm telling you to get down!

797
01:12:32.583 --> 01:12:34.708
All right! You're done.

798
01:12:35.208 --> 01:12:37.541
I came to train with my partner.

799
01:12:37.625 --> 01:12:40.458
- You're done for today.
- We're only weeks away...

800
01:12:40.541 --> 01:12:43.208
- Get out of the pool!
- from the Olympics!

801
01:12:43.291 --> 01:12:46.958
Get out right now or you'll be expelled!

802
01:12:47.041 --> 01:12:49.083
What do you say? Right now!

803
01:12:50.083 --> 01:12:51.166
Get out!

804
01:12:52.750 --> 01:12:54.625
And don't think of coming here

805
01:12:54.708 --> 01:12:58.166
if you're not willing
to follow my fucking orders!

806
01:13:34.750 --> 01:13:39.541
Would you like to eat anything?
Gerardo took your siblings to a game.

807
01:14:08.958 --> 01:14:11.833
- Are you okay, Yeya?
- Not now, Mom.

808
01:14:11.916 --> 01:14:13.500
What's going on, honey?

809
01:14:14.500 --> 01:14:16.125
Please, I want to be alone.

810
01:14:19.333 --> 01:14:20.875
What's going on, Mariel?

811
01:14:20.958 --> 01:14:22.916
I don't want to talk right now.

812
01:14:23.791 --> 01:14:29.083
We have to talk.
I won't let you do what you always do.

813
01:14:30.791 --> 01:14:34.166
What I always do?
What the fuck are you talking about?

814
01:14:34.250 --> 01:14:35.875
You're sabotaging yourself.

815
01:14:35.958 --> 01:14:39.916
The Olympic Games are near,
and you've become self-destructive.

816
01:14:40.000 --> 01:14:42.000
Where did you get that shit from?

817
01:14:42.625 --> 01:14:46.291
Braulio called this afternoon
and said you were out of control.

818
01:14:46.375 --> 01:14:48.666
Leave before anything happens.

819
01:14:48.750 --> 01:14:52.083
I'm not going anywhere
until you explain to me

820
01:14:52.166 --> 01:14:55.208
why you're destroying
everything you've built.

821
01:14:57.041 --> 01:15:00.250
- Stop it, for fuck's sake!
- Don't talk to me like that!

822
01:15:00.333 --> 01:15:02.958
You want to know
what's happening? All right!

823
01:15:10.166 --> 01:15:13.000
The great mystery
is that you were there, right?

824
01:15:13.666 --> 01:15:16.166
Every year, in every fucking tournament,

825
01:15:17.625 --> 01:15:19.250
you were there.

826
01:15:19.333 --> 01:15:24.000
Or he was here, because he's family,
because we're a fucking happy family.

827
01:15:28.000 --> 01:15:29.875
How could you not know, Mom?

828
01:15:35.666 --> 01:15:38.750
"Easy, girl, you rock here."

829
01:15:38.833 --> 01:15:42.500
"If you make a good dive,
"I'll make you feel real good."

830
01:15:42.583 --> 01:15:44.708
"I'll teach you how to be my woman."

831
01:15:45.291 --> 01:15:46.625
What's wrong with you?

832
01:15:46.708 --> 01:15:48.666
"You taste so good, girl."

833
01:15:48.750 --> 01:15:50.125
You're messed up.

834
01:15:51.250 --> 01:15:53.375
"You'll never find someone like me."

835
01:15:53.458 --> 01:15:56.083
How can you say something so appalling?

836
01:15:57.500 --> 01:16:00.500
- "I can't live without you, girl."
- You're so sick!

837
01:16:04.000 --> 01:16:06.458
Didn't you want to know
what was going on?

838
01:16:07.333 --> 01:16:09.041
That's what happened,

839
01:16:10.166 --> 01:16:12.958
right under your fucking nose,
the whole time.

840
01:16:19.250 --> 01:16:21.375
Why did you let me go to Monterrey?

841
01:16:24.541 --> 01:16:27.166
You were supposed to take care of me.

842
01:16:36.458 --> 01:16:37.500
Mom!

843
01:16:54.708 --> 01:16:56.125
You scared me to death!

844
01:16:57.125 --> 01:16:58.125
Sorry.

845
01:17:05.583 --> 01:17:08.250
- Nadia was worried too.
- Why?

846
01:17:09.333 --> 01:17:11.916
"Why?" You're a team, right?

847
01:17:15.250 --> 01:17:19.166
Are you ready to do team work
or are we still having issues?

848
01:17:19.250 --> 01:17:20.375
No issues.

849
01:17:22.750 --> 01:17:25.083
Stop, Braulio, let me go!

850
01:17:27.916 --> 01:17:31.833
I'll see you in 20 at the pool.
Everybody to the pool!

851
01:17:32.416 --> 01:17:36.791
Remember, arms, with strength!

852
01:17:36.875 --> 01:17:40.541
Approach straight up. Jump!

853
01:17:40.625 --> 01:17:41.916
Like that!

854
01:17:43.458 --> 01:17:44.708
Again!

855
01:17:46.083 --> 01:17:47.458
Again!

856
01:17:49.791 --> 01:17:52.791
Nadia, your face! That's right!

857
01:17:56.708 --> 01:17:59.500
Please, focus!

858
01:18:03.875 --> 01:18:08.000
You're not in sync, please!

859
01:18:14.458 --> 01:18:15.666
Push the platform.

860
01:18:15.750 --> 01:18:18.541
Rib tuck. Look for the water and flex.

861
01:18:21.125 --> 01:18:24.625
- Who told you to stop?
- Nadia is tired.

862
01:18:24.708 --> 01:18:26.208
Did I tell you to stop?

863
01:18:31.500 --> 01:18:34.791
Come on! We can't be doing this all day!

864
01:18:40.916 --> 01:18:43.458
Watch out! You were ahead.

865
01:18:44.125 --> 01:18:47.041
If you want to chat, go to a caf!

866
01:18:51.291 --> 01:18:52.875
Arms! With strength!

867
01:18:55.166 --> 01:18:56.166
Again!

868
01:18:56.708 --> 01:18:57.750
You count.

869
01:19:03.041 --> 01:19:04.375
One, two.

870
01:19:12.750 --> 01:19:15.541
- Damn! That's worth the gold!
- Come on, team!

871
01:19:15.625 --> 01:19:19.916
Motherfucker! Excellent, I see gold now!

872
01:19:25.625 --> 01:19:29.375
Did you pack already?
I already packed mine.

873
01:19:29.458 --> 01:19:31.333
My dad says that's ridiculous,

874
01:19:31.416 --> 01:19:34.958
because me and my mom pack
two days before the trip

875
01:19:35.041 --> 01:19:36.708
so we don't forget anything.

876
01:19:37.416 --> 01:19:39.041
Do you think it'll be cold?

877
01:19:39.583 --> 01:19:42.958
- I searched on the Internet...
- I know about Braulio.

878
01:19:46.291 --> 01:19:48.083
I don't know what you mean.

879
01:19:49.708 --> 01:19:51.500
The same happened to me.

880
01:19:57.250 --> 01:19:58.250
Nadia.

881
01:20:06.000 --> 01:20:08.000
Nadia, please, let me help you.

882
01:20:08.083 --> 01:20:09.625
I don't need your help.

883
01:20:12.250 --> 01:20:13.791
What he's doing is wrong.

884
01:20:14.750 --> 01:20:18.041
He's our coach. He's an adult.
And you're a little girl.

885
01:20:19.583 --> 01:20:20.916
I'm not a little girl.

886
01:20:21.000 --> 01:20:25.166
You're 14, I was your same age.
But I was all alone, and you are not.

887
01:20:25.250 --> 01:20:29.166
- You don't get what happens between us.
- I perfectly get it.

888
01:20:30.125 --> 01:20:32.416
He's telling you that you rock,

889
01:20:32.500 --> 01:20:35.291
that you're special
and there's no one like you,

890
01:20:35.375 --> 01:20:38.291
that you must keep the secret
because they won't get it.

891
01:20:38.375 --> 01:20:40.875
I perfectly know what he's telling you.

892
01:20:40.958 --> 01:20:44.541
Braulio was right.
He said you'd try to screw everything up.

893
01:20:44.625 --> 01:20:47.500
You're so damn jealous! I don't care!

894
01:20:47.583 --> 01:20:50.916
Back from Greece,
we'll get married and he'll be with me.

895
01:20:51.000 --> 01:20:52.333
He's leaving his wife.

896
01:21:19.166 --> 01:21:20.166
What happened?

897
01:21:21.791 --> 01:21:23.333
You have to take a shower.

898
01:21:24.375 --> 01:21:26.291
Today's the press conference.

899
01:21:31.083 --> 01:21:32.500
Braulio came to see you.

900
01:21:34.666 --> 01:21:35.666
He's downstairs.

901
01:21:37.958 --> 01:21:39.375
He wants to talk to you.

902
01:21:41.958 --> 01:21:43.208
He called last night.

903
01:21:44.958 --> 01:21:47.583
I think you need
to apologize to him, Mariel.

904
01:21:51.833 --> 01:21:53.500
We're so close, honey.

905
01:22:23.125 --> 01:22:25.625
- If you came to threaten me...
- No, Mariel.

906
01:22:27.833 --> 01:22:29.208
I came to apologize.

907
01:22:34.500 --> 01:22:35.500
Forgive me.

908
01:22:40.958 --> 01:22:42.291
Forgive me, please.

909
01:22:44.791 --> 01:22:46.625
I was so confused.

910
01:22:48.791 --> 01:22:50.208
And now I realize

911
01:22:52.083 --> 01:22:54.250
that I've become a monster.

912
01:22:59.083 --> 01:23:00.666
I am a human being

913
01:23:02.541 --> 01:23:05.000
with flaws and weaknesses,

914
01:23:07.208 --> 01:23:10.708
but I don't want that to justify
all the damage I've done,

915
01:23:12.291 --> 01:23:13.708
especially to you, girl.

916
01:23:15.041 --> 01:23:16.416
Forgive me, please.

917
01:23:19.708 --> 01:23:21.041
You're Mariel.

918
01:23:21.916 --> 01:23:23.166
My Mariel.

919
01:23:26.041 --> 01:23:29.083
We had a very special relationship, girl.

920
01:23:32.708 --> 01:23:34.000
And I miss it.

921
01:23:34.875 --> 01:23:36.250
I miss it so much.

922
01:23:38.041 --> 01:23:39.375
I need you.

923
01:23:40.041 --> 01:23:42.083
And I know you need me too.

924
01:23:44.791 --> 01:23:46.875
You and I are meant for each other.

925
01:23:48.291 --> 01:23:49.291
Please.

926
01:23:52.041 --> 01:23:54.166
Let's give ourselves another chance.

927
01:23:58.125 --> 01:23:59.750
We have to be together.

928
01:24:00.708 --> 01:24:02.666
Don't you ever touch me again...

929
01:24:06.875 --> 01:24:08.250
in your fucking life.

930
01:24:13.250 --> 01:24:14.791
Don't ever touch me again.

931
01:24:22.791 --> 01:24:24.166
Do you want your medal?

932
01:24:27.208 --> 01:24:29.291
Don't you dare touch her.

933
01:24:31.791 --> 01:24:37.041
If you get close to her again,
I'll tell everything to everyone.

934
01:24:39.750 --> 01:24:42.875
I don't give a fuck
if my life goes down with yours.

935
01:24:48.208 --> 01:24:49.208
I mean it.

936
01:24:59.083 --> 01:25:01.625
We want to honor these athletes

937
01:25:01.708 --> 01:25:04.875
who are traveling to Greece tomorrow

938
01:25:04.958 --> 01:25:10.875
to represent Mexico
in the 2004 Summer Olympics in Athens.

939
01:25:10.958 --> 01:25:12.958
A round of applause, please!

940
01:25:13.041 --> 01:25:14.875
Bravo!

941
01:25:24.000 --> 01:25:27.500
We're very proud to represent our country.

942
01:25:29.791 --> 01:25:32.000
- My pleasure.
- Good luck, Mariel.

943
01:25:32.083 --> 01:25:35.333
All right, kids, it's time! Let's go!

944
01:25:36.458 --> 01:25:38.333
I'm so proud of you, honey.

945
01:25:38.916 --> 01:25:40.125
Let's go, kids!

946
01:25:41.625 --> 01:25:45.458
Mexico!

947
01:25:56.583 --> 01:25:57.583
Irene.

948
01:26:02.791 --> 01:26:03.958
Forgive me.

949
01:27:25.625 --> 01:27:28.375
From Greece, Eftihia Pappa

950
01:27:29.666 --> 01:27:31.708
and Florentia Sfakianou.

951
01:27:32.583 --> 01:27:35.666
From Mexico, Mariel Saenz

952
01:27:36.541 --> 01:27:38.500
and Nadia Alfaro.

953
01:27:53.958 --> 01:27:58.208
Mariel has achieved the best performance
in her whole career.

954
01:27:58.291 --> 01:28:00.333
We'll see the Mexican duet.

955
01:28:00.416 --> 01:28:05.416
A brilliant duet formed
by expertise and youth.

956
01:28:05.500 --> 01:28:08.875
They'll perform the last dive.

957
01:28:09.500 --> 01:28:13.166
A dive with a great level of difficulty.

958
01:28:13.250 --> 01:28:16.625
They already dominate this technique,

959
01:28:16.708 --> 01:28:19.833
despite the short time
they've been training together.

960
01:28:19.916 --> 01:28:22.333
It's the last dive of the competition.

961
01:28:22.416 --> 01:28:25.291
All Mexico's watching what could be

962
01:28:25.375 --> 01:28:29.208
the first medal
for the Mexican Olympic Team.

963
01:28:30.208 --> 01:28:32.500
I WANT TO SCREAM

964
01:28:46.125 --> 01:28:49.000
I'd have liked to do something before,

965
01:28:49.083 --> 01:28:50.416
but I couldn't.

966
01:29:11.916 --> 01:29:14.291
What? How? This can't be true!

967
01:29:14.416 --> 01:29:17.708
This is really extraordinary!

968
01:29:21.791 --> 01:29:24.458
It doesn't seem to be an injury,

969
01:29:24.541 --> 01:29:26.958
but something must have happened

970
01:29:27.041 --> 01:29:30.083
because Mexico is leaving
without its medal.

971
01:29:36.375 --> 01:29:40.000
Braulio Peralta told me
he'd never met anyone like me,

972
01:29:40.083 --> 01:29:42.916
something that surely
he also told your daughter.

973
01:29:43.916 --> 01:29:46.333
If it hadn't been for Nadia,

974
01:29:46.416 --> 01:29:49.583
I might never have woken up
from this nightmare.

975
01:29:50.875 --> 01:29:53.750
The only thing I can give her
is the truth,

976
01:29:54.833 --> 01:29:59.041
and hope she can run away
before this hell consumes her alive.

977
01:33:15.250 --> 01:33:20.750
Subtitle translation by Mariana G. Bentez